                <h1>Professors weigh in on NASA discovery of seven exoplanets</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/59ed8a21-969b-4db2-9019-ff201934d958.sized-1000x1000.png?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Last&#x20;month,&#x20;NASA&amp;nbsp&#x3B;discovered&#x20;seven&#x20;exoplanets&amp;nbsp&#x3B;rotating&#x20;around&#x20;a&#x20;star&amp;nbsp&#x3B;called&#x20;TRAPPIST-1.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Last month, NASA&nbsp;discovered seven exoplanets&nbsp;rotating around a star&nbsp;called TRAPPIST-1.</p>

                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/rob-palmisano">Rob Palmisano</a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">March 13, 2017 | 12:32am EDT</span>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-left text-md-right d-print-none">
                            <ul class="social-links list-unsyled list-inline mt-4 mt-md-0">
                                <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://www.dukechronicle.com/article/2017/03/professors-weigh-in-on-nasa-discovery-of-seven-exoplanets" target="_blank" class="sends-events" data-ga-category="Share" data-ga-action="click" data-ga-label="facebook" data-ga-value="CURL"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a></li>
